    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p>Never published before this edition.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name>Εὔδ<unclear>ω</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ρος</supplied></name></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Θαυμ-"><seg part="I">Θαυ<supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied></seg><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></name></persName>
                    <lb n="2a"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/><certainty locus="name" match=".."/>
                </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Eudoros, Thaum<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
           <p>Eudoros, Thaum<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Eudoros, Thaum<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p/>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
             <p>At line 1 it would also be theoretically possible to read the name <foreign xml:lang="grc">Θεύδωρος</foreign> with one letter missing at left. However, that is less probable because 
             at line 2 we do have, slightly farther to the right, the beginning of another personal name. For the latter, related to the stem of <foreign xml:lang="grc">θαῦμα</foreign>, several names are possible. The 
             only other occurrence in Cyrenaica is also incomplete (<ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr084000</ref> a.74).</p>
            </div></body>
